title: Binance Spars With U.S. Regulators Over Asset Freeze
description: A judge urged the Securities and Exchange Commission to reach a compromise with Binance that would allow the world’s largest cryptocurrency exchange to continue operating in the United States.

title: In Milan, Putting an A.I. Travel Assistant to the Test
description: On her first visit to the northern Italian city, our reporter compares the itineraries of two travel advisers: one virtual, the other human. Here’s what she found.
